 <a rel="nofollow" href="https://frosty.media">Frosty Media</a>.</p>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6:"Austin";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:6210:"<p class="alert">This plugin is an extension and requires <a href="https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/" title="Custom Login">Custom Login</a> (version <strong>3.x</strong>) which can be downloaded for free <a href="https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/">here</a>.</p><p>Have you wanted to add that extra touch to your WordPress login page? Have you been looking for ways to customize every part of your site to your personal or business brand? </p>\n<p>My guess is you&#8217;ve answered yes to one of those questions. With <a href="http://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login/" title="Custom Login 3.0">Custom Login</a> it&#8217;s easy to brand your login page with the change of a few settings.</p>\n<h3>Adding Custom Style</h3>\n<p>What this style pack offers is four customized settings that you could activate at the click of a button. Upon activation you can do nothing and enjoy the new custom login style or tinker with the settings by adding your own logo or additional CSS, HTML or jQuery.</p>\n<h4>#1 The <em>Light Blue Slide In</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src="https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-style-light-blue-slide-in.gif" alt="Light Blue Style Pack w/ Slide in CSS3 animation" width="640" height="480" class="size-full wp-image-25968" /><br />\n<em>This style pack is light but packs a blue punch. The form will slide in with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h4>#2 The <em>Jagged Zoom Right In</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src="https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-style-jagged-zoom-right-in.gif" alt="Jagged Rock Style Pack w/ Zoom right in CSS3 animation" width="640" height="480" class="size-full wp-image-25976" /><br />\n<em>This style pack is has soft earth colors but has that sharpe jagged edge. The form will slide in with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h4>#3 The <em>Wood Fade In Down</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src="https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-style-wood-fade-in-down.gif" alt="Wood Style Pack w/ Fade in Down CSS3 animation" width="640" height="480" class="size-full wp-image-25969" /><br />\n<em>This style pack is rich with a dynamic wood background. The form will slide in with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h4>#4 The <em>Fog Fade In Up</em> Style</h4>\n<p><img src="https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-style-fog-fade-in-up.gif" alt="Fog Style Pack w/ Fade in up CSS3 animation" width="640" height="480" class="size-full wp-image-25966" /><br />\n<em>This style pack has that dark secretive vibe. The form will slide in with CSS3 animation.</em></p>\n<h3>How-to install</h3>\n<p>Follow this <a href="//frosty.media/docs/installing-custom-login-extensions/">documentation</a> guide.</p>\n<h3>Screenshots</h3>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-login-gray-fog/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-login-gray-fog-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Custom Login Style Pack - Fog" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-login-jagged-rock/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-login-jagged-rock-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Custom Login Style Pack - Jagged Rock" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-login-light-blue/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-login-light-blue-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Custom Login Style Pack - Light Blue" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-login-style-pack-settings-1/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-login-style-pack-settings-1-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Custom Login Style Pack Settings" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-login-style-pack-settings-2/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-login-style-pack-settings-2-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Custom Login Style Pack Settings - Activate button" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-login-wood/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-login-wood-150x150.png" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Custom Login Style Pack - Wood" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-style-fog-fade-in-up/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-style-fog-fade-in-up-150x150.gif" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Fog Style Pack w/ Fade in up CSS3 animation" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-style-light-blue-slide-in/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/cl-style-light-blue-slide-in-150x150.gif" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Light Blue Style Pack w/ Slide in CSS3 animation" /></a>\n<a href=''https://frosty.media/plugins/custom-login-style-pack-1/cl-style-wood-fade-in-down/''><img width="150" height="150" src="https://8527-presscdn-0-97-pagely