(2153, 1, '2015-11-10 07:48:27', '2015-11-10 13:48:27', 'This post should display a <a title="Featured Images" href="http://en.support.wordpress.com/featured-images/#setting-a-featured-image" target="_blank">featured image</a>, if the theme <a title="Post Thumbnails" href="http://codex.wordpress.org/Post_Thumbnails" target="_blank">supports it</a>.\n\nNon-square images can provide some unique styling issues.\n\nThis post tests a vertical featured image.', 'Template: Featured Image (Vertical)', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1016-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-11-10 07:48:27', '2015-11-10 13:48:27', '', 1016, 'http://localhost/widget-pc/wordpress-base/1016-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
